parameters.name: ChanelType
parameters.description:
The alert notification method. Valid values:

*   Mail: emails
*   DingWebHook: DingTalk chatbots

parameters.name: ChanelValue
parameters.description:
The value specified for the alert notification method.

>  This parameter is required only if you set the `ChanelType` parameter to `Mail`.

parameters.name: ContactName
parameters.description: The name of the alert contact.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description:
The number of the page to return.

Default value: 1.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of entries to return on each page.

Default value: 100.
